From 38686f48ca174e2249843b2e4655995c0c8b38b4 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Tue, 14 Jul 2026 14:26:24 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/5] feat: plain-text indexing, country metadata, document
 CRUD and stats endpoints

Fase 1 of the plain-text manager plan:
- POST /index: normalize plain text, tenant-scoped SHA256 dedup, hybrid
  chunking, batch embeddings, TurboVec add + PostgreSQL metadata, with
  deterministic 63-bit chunk ids (idempotent retries, no id coordination)
- BibliographicMetadata gains country; ORM column bib_country; dynamic
  case-insensitive filters (idioma, tema, institucion, pais) in
  GET /documents
- GET /documents/{id} (chunk count included), DELETE /documents/{id}
  (tenant-scoped, vectors first then metadata), GET /stats (corpus counts,
  index dimension/version)
- plain-text normalizer separate from the PDF header/footer stripper
- in-memory port fakes + end-to-end API tests; 184 tests green

Co-Authored-By: Claude Fable 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
